response.original_title: Berryz Koubou Debut 10 Shuunen Kinen Special Concert 2014 Thank you BeriKyuu! in Nippon Budokan "Kouhen"
response.overview: Berryz Koubou Debut 10 Shuunen Kinen Special Concert 2014 Thank you BeriKyuu! in Nippon Budokan "Kouhen" is Berryz Koubou's second Nippon Budokan live concert. It took place on September 11, 2014.
